message.en_US: Hello and welcome to the \c[1]Vermillion Training Facility\c[0]!
Here at the Vermillion Training Facility, We train seekers like you to expand your abilities and more.
You can use the \c[2]Advanced Training Terminal \c[0]in my left to start the training!
Do you want to know how the Challenge System Works?
Challenges are separated by floors, and each floor will have a difficulty.
Each difficulty will change the type of challenge you are doing making the challenge always look different from the others.

For an example this \c[3]Challenge \c[0]is the Cold challenge. You will be locked only to \i[element-cold]\c[3]Cold \c[0]to defeat enemies. The only way to defeat them is using the \i[element-heat]\c[3]Heat Ball Changers \c[0]in the arena, and the difficulty of this Challenge is 1.
Also there is 2 waves of enemies. The first one being the "Kill All" type and the other being a \c[1]Boss\c[0]
Have a good day and stay vigilant!
